---
title: Mild Indian White Fish Curry with Roasted Veggies & Basmati Rice
description: A mild heat from the curry mixed in with fresh fish and veggies is a power battle that you don’t want to miss because
both will be fighting for your tastebuds’ attention. In the end, both the soothing curry and rejuvenating white fish are
winners and that’s why this dinner will come out on top!

